Package: neonNitrate
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Dashboard for Surface Water Nitrate Data Analysis in Germany
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Rimlan Lora",
      family = "Alva",
      email = "ralv0004@student.monash.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides interactive tools and visualizations for exploring surface water nitrate concentrations from the NEON project across German monitoring sites.
 Includes real-time dashboards, summary statistics, population burden estimates, and stratified analysis features for research and educational use.
 Designed to support flexible data upload and filtering, with professional-grade plots, tables, and output interpretation.
